Paper: hep-th/0105253

Date: 2001-05-24

Title: On the Gauge Invariance of the Chern-Simons Action for N D-Branes

Authors: Calin Ciocarlie

Comments: 15 pages

Journal-ref: JHEP 0107 (2001) 028

In this short note we provide a proof that the Chern-Simons part of theaction for N D-branes is invariant under gauge transformations of the RR fieldsof the type C_p ->C_p + d\Lambda_{p-1}, and rewrite the action in a form thatmakes this symmetry manifest.